description=<p>The U3 Example is a simple music player application for U3 drives. This PDF shows you how to use this sample proejct and how to build applications for U3 in Revolution. We recommend that you have explored the introductory video tutorials so you have a basic understanding of how Revolution works before you start on the sample projects.</p>
